<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>苏西在厨房里玩儿拼图。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喵！”她的猫用爪子挠后门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你现在不能出去，雪球。”苏西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喵！”雪球又挠了几下门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在不行，雪球。”苏西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你刚剃了毛……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喵！”突然，雪球长出了锋利的牙齿和尖尖的毛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！雪球吐出一个燃烧的毛球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>厨房里到处都是烟雾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当烟雾散去时，门不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪球也不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“坐下，麦克斯！”玛拉说，“坐下！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和她的朋友们在美罗城公园里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在训练玛拉家的新狗，麦克斯，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是麦克斯不听话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“麦克斯，你给我坐下。”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“汪！”麦克斯叫了一声，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后它趴下，打了个呵欠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“坐着对麦克斯来讲也许太无聊了。”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得教它一些有意思的技能。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克跑到一棵树那儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“麦克斯！”他叫道，“过来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麦克斯翻了个身，侧躺着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔伸出他的手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把你的爪子给我，麦克斯。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麦克斯站起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它喜欢这个技能！”特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，麦克斯只是挠了挠耳朵后面，又趴下了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉叹了口气。“真是没希望了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麦克斯什么技能也学不会。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克在麦克斯旁边坐下，摸了摸它的头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我相信麦克斯能学会技能。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它只是需要时间。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西挠了挠麦克斯耳朵后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“麦克斯是一只很棒的宠物，玛拉。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它只是有点儿……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“无聊。”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“无聊也没什么不对。”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉皱起眉头。“我希望麦克斯是最棒的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊！有一只最棒的狗很酷！”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们也许可以让火箭女孩儿来训练麦克斯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她可以让麦克斯变成真正‘最棒的’！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得火箭女孩儿不会训练宠物，特勒尔。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说的也对。”特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他摸了摸麦克斯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跳起来。“我刚刚想起来了，玛拉！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麦克斯肯定会一个技能。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么技能？”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的眼睛亮了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西严肃地看着麦克斯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“麦克斯，别动！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个时候，麦克斯正安静地打着呼噜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它一动不动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看到了吧？”罗西笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔和杰克大笑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，罗西听到她的手表在响。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西离开了朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长。”罗西低声说，“有什么问题吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“出现了严重的问题，火箭女孩儿！”市长大声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，怪兽宠物在西街上到处跑！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>